response.original_title: Travis Tritt's Greatest Hits: From the Beginning
response.overview: Featuring music videos for several of his chart-topping hits, this compilation showcases why Grammy Award winner Travis Tritt is one of the biggest superstars country music has ever produced. Highlights include "Country Club," "Tell Me I Was Dreaming," "Put Some Drive in Your Country," "Anymore," "T-R-O-U-B-L-E," "Foolish Pride," "Here's a Quarter" and the hit Marty Stewart duet "The Whiskey Ain't Working."
response.title: Travis Tritt's Greatest Hits: From the Beginning
